dshift. Finally, we\nreport that one of the new z_abs ~ z_em DLAs discovered by CORALS has some\nresidual flux in the base of the Lya trough which may be due to Lya emission,\neither from star formation in the DLA galaxy or from gas photoionised by the\nQSO.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Dec 2001 12:09:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
